messages.message: Release notes for weds (internal only) release in :thread::

*Release for Weds*
• App runs will be _mostly_ feature complete, enabled via toggle in product: 
    ◦ All field types except for reasoning and visual reasoning
    ◦ Cleans & Validations (except for those based on confidence rules)
• Ground truth accuracy tooling will also be feature complete, enabled via toggle in product
• Not yet available: DocAI enabled in Build; Provenance; Confidence scores
